        <td>
          <para styleclass="Interface">SELECTION-WINDOW <text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">is at </text><text styleclass="Popup Box">the top of the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MechDesigner-ProjectExplorer" styleclass="Popup Box2">Project-Explorer</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface"><text styleclass="Popup Box">It shows the elements that you </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">click</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Graphic-Area" styleclass="Popup Box2">graphic-area</link><text styleclass="Popup Box">, the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Assembly-Tree" styleclass="Popup Box2">Assembly-Tree</link><text styleclass="Popup Box">, </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Kinematics-Tree" styleclass="Popup Box2">Kinematics-Tree</link><text styleclass="Popup Box2">, </text><text styleclass="Popup Box">or the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Geometry-Tree" styleclass="Popup Box2">Geometry-Tree</link><text styleclass="Popup Box">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Right-click</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> any element in the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Selection-Window</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> to show a contextual menu. Use this menu to:</text></para>
          <list id="37" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Edit</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Delete</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rename</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Show the Element&apos;s References.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-View-References">Show Element References</link></para>
